WEBVTT

00:01:35.560 --> 00:01:38.120
Mr. Martin's life began with

00:01:38.120 --> 00:01:41.000
his most enduring quality: kindness.

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:42.920
From Goldman Sachs to Morgan Stanley,

00:01:43.120 --> 00:01:46.040
from investment bank partner to Nasdaq bell-ringer,

00:01:46.239 --> 00:01:48.640
such a life has only one ending:

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:51.640
decomposition into inorganic salts, carbon dioxide, and water.

00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:53.000
And I

00:01:53.000 --> 00:01:54.719
seem to have reached this day.

00:01:54.719 --> 00:01:56.159
How faith and hope begin with oneself

00:01:56.159 --> 00:01:57.920
and then flow to others.

00:01:58.280 --> 00:02:00.879
He shared a better version of himself with us,

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:02.359
promises,

00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:03.319
happiness,

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:04.680
and love.

00:02:05.120 --> 00:02:07.599
May the deceased rest in peace.

00:02:08.520 --> 00:02:10.639
Lying in a coffin doesn't necessarily mean peace.

00:02:11.280 --> 00:02:14.000
See this strange little peak on the deathbed ECG?

00:02:14.199 --> 00:02:16.039
This isn't some final rally.

00:02:16.680 --> 00:02:18.879
It's this little tormentor, like a black square,

00:02:18.879 --> 00:02:20.000
telling you,

00:02:20.319 --> 00:02:21.319
"You're not off work yet."

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:29.840
What's up, Kong Liang?

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:30.479
Mr. Ma.

00:02:30.759 --> 00:02:32.080
The meeting is about to start.

00:02:32.080 --> 00:02:33.159
Jack is already here.

00:02:33.159 --> 00:02:34.400
Mr. Zhang will be here shortly.

00:02:34.479 --> 00:02:35.439
Is everything ready?

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:36.520
Everything is ready.

00:02:36.840 --> 00:02:38.120
Alright, I'll be right there.

00:02:39.520 --> 00:02:40.400
Martin.

00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:41.759
How are you feeling?

00:02:43.319 --> 00:02:44.479
Keep the doves.

00:02:44.680 --> 00:02:46.319
But lose the choir and the pastor.

00:02:48.400 --> 00:02:49.599
The list of friends and relatives attending the funeral,

00:02:49.599 --> 00:02:50.800
please give it to us as soon as possible.

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:52.960
Especially those from China, we need to prepare in advance.

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:54.800
No one will attend.

00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:56.400
How is that possible?

00:02:56.479 --> 00:02:58.400
It's inconvenient to come from China, fine.

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:00.120
But you've been in the US for so many years.

00:03:00.280 --> 00:03:02.000
You're a senior executive at a big company.

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:03.560
Don't you have any friends?

00:03:03.960 --> 00:03:05.120
Not needed, thank you.

00:03:08.479 --> 00:03:09.960
Don't you have any friends?

00:03:11.080 --> 00:03:11.879
My God.

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:13.879
This is in Manhattan, New York.

00:03:13.879 --> 00:03:15.199
The most artificial,

00:03:15.199 --> 00:03:16.719
most impersonal street in the world.

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:19.879
Hearing the funeral director mention the word "friend"

00:03:19.879 --> 00:03:22.479
feels like something from a past life to me.

00:03:23.439 --> 00:03:24.840
I once had friends too.

00:03:25.319 --> 00:03:27.159
Though now we are estranged,

00:03:27.639 --> 00:03:30.199
they wouldn't even attend my funeral.

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:33.080
But looking back now,

00:03:33.639 --> 00:03:35.360
the happiest times of my life

00:03:35.719 --> 00:03:38.439
were running with them every day in Baofang Hutong,

00:03:38.719 --> 00:03:40.439
those days of youthful ignorance.

00:03:40.759 --> 00:03:43.159
It seemed like it was always summer then.

00:03:44.599 --> 00:03:46.000
Arctic Ocean soda,

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:48.199
big watermelons soaking in Houhai Lake.

00:03:49.199 --> 00:03:50.919
On the last day of my life,

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:53.000
I actually find myself missing it quite a bit.

00:03:54.280 --> 00:03:54.960
By the way,

00:03:55.280 --> 00:03:56.879
I heard my three brothers

00:03:56.879 --> 00:03:59.680
are now doing quite well back in China.

00:04:00.639 --> 00:04:03.439
Our Chinese culture is profound

00:04:03.639 --> 00:04:05.120
and has a long history.

00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:07.759
Now, I will use this bowl of congee

00:04:07.879 --> 00:04:10.560
to offer you all my most sincere blessings.

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:12.000
Working at a big tech firm,

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:13.240
reaching middle management.

00:04:14.439 --> 00:04:16.680
He might be a smooth, versatile business genius.

00:04:16.680 --> 00:04:17.439
This

00:04:17.839 --> 00:04:19.879
represents the two focal points of the Yin-Yang symbol.

00:04:20.399 --> 00:04:23.480
Symbolizing unique insight and foresight.

00:04:23.480 --> 00:04:24.199
Or perhaps

00:04:24.199 --> 00:04:24.920
First, for you two.

00:04:24.920 --> 00:04:26.319
he's a scheming workplace expert.

00:04:26.319 --> 00:04:26.879
As the saying goes,

00:04:26.879 --> 00:04:29.519
"Solitary Yin does not grow, lone Yang does not birth."

00:04:29.920 --> 00:04:32.199
This cycle of Yin and Yang

00:04:32.279 --> 00:04:34.279
is what brings harmony and stability.

00:04:35.319 --> 00:04:36.920
Our Director Liu's work

00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:38.240
is of utmost importance.

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:39.160
Forget it, I can't keep this up.

00:04:39.160 --> 00:04:39.759
You flatter me, no, no.

00:04:39.879 --> 00:04:41.000
To be honest,

00:04:41.000 --> 00:04:43.199
he's really stupid, dull, and annoying.

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:43.720
You're too kind.

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:44.360
And hyper-masculine.

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:51.600
Let me tell you this.

00:04:51.879 --> 00:04:52.959
We,

00:04:53.279 --> 00:04:55.759
Cambridge, Harvard, Oxford...

00:04:56.399 --> 00:04:57.639
Our Wang Fei,

00:04:57.639 --> 00:04:59.959
his academic performance is absolutely no problem.

00:04:59.959 --> 00:05:01.959
A top bird, a duck king for the ages.

00:05:01.959 --> 00:05:02.560
Alright then.

00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:03.720
Okay, thank you for your trouble.

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:05.279
Don't misunderstand, he's the descendant of a famous chef.

00:05:05.519 --> 00:05:07.639
And he does have some skills.

00:05:07.639 --> 00:05:09.800
One for scrubbing pots, one for brushing oil.

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:11.399
Come on, lift your shirt.

00:05:11.480 --> 00:05:12.839
The gel is a bit cold.

00:05:13.800 --> 00:05:15.120
Why are you wearing sunglasses?

00:05:15.120 --> 00:05:16.279
Are you embarrassed?

00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:18.759
No, it's just... we're too familiar, you know?

00:05:24.399 --> 00:05:25.839
Director Qiu, I'm at the door.

00:05:25.839 --> 00:05:28.040
The door is closed. Are you inside?

00:05:29.079 --> 00:05:30.759
The previous one was for preparing the duck.

00:05:30.879 --> 00:05:31.560
Okay, okay.

00:05:31.560 --> 00:05:32.600
This one now is for slacking off.

00:05:32.600 --> 00:05:33.240
But it seems

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:34.079
Let me see...

00:05:34.279 --> 00:05:35.839
he never slacks off at the right time.

00:05:36.480 --> 00:05:38.319
Trying to discuss wealth management with these people,

00:05:38.600 --> 00:05:40.480
I'm afraid you won't get out without losing a layer of skin.

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:42.720
Fishing in troubled waters, be careful not to twist your ankle.

00:05:42.920 --> 00:05:45.199
Sisters, let's get hyped!

00:05:45.199 --> 00:05:46.079
Hello.

00:05:46.480 --> 00:05:47.720
Is Director Qiu in?

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:51.319
You... who are you looking for?

00:05:51.319 --> 00:05:52.399
Looking for Director Qiu.

00:05:53.360 --> 00:05:54.759
Slow down, slow down, slow down.

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:02.839
I'll go find her for you.

00:06:03.639 --> 00:06:04.680
Unfortunately,

00:06:05.279 --> 00:06:07.079
that matter between me and them

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:09.399
ultimately had no chance to be resolved.

00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:18.519
Hello, Martin.

00:06:18.519 --> 00:06:19.199
Good morning.

00:06:21.240 --> 00:06:21.959
Director Zhang.

00:06:22.519 --> 00:06:24.959
We reviewed the data from the past two years.

00:06:24.959 --> 00:06:26.399
Under Martin's leadership,

00:06:26.399 --> 00:06:28.680
business growth has been very slow.

00:06:29.439 --> 00:06:31.639
This is complete inaction.

00:06:31.639 --> 00:06:32.720
I propose

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:35.800
the board dismisses Martin from his position.

00:06:38.360 --> 00:06:39.800
That old fool Jack

00:06:39.800 --> 00:06:41.839
probably still thinks he has the upper hand.

00:06:41.920 --> 00:06:43.879
He thinks he bribed my people,

00:06:44.120 --> 00:06:45.240
little does he know

00:06:45.240 --> 00:06:46.480
the words in their hands

00:06:46.480 --> 00:06:47.439
and the evidence in their pockets

00:06:47.439 --> 00:06:49.160
were all fuses I handed over.

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:53.879
Martin,

00:06:55.800 --> 00:06:57.319
you set me up.

00:07:01.959 --> 00:07:03.560
Fine.

00:07:04.959 --> 00:07:06.759
Spare me this once, okay?

00:07:07.199 --> 00:07:07.879
I'm sorry.

00:07:09.319 --> 00:07:11.800
Idiot, get back to your country.

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:14.560
But as you wish.

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:19.360
I kind of regret it.

00:07:19.839 --> 00:07:21.639
I should feel sympathy for old Jack right now.

00:07:22.120 --> 00:07:23.720
His situation is truly difficult.

00:07:24.680 --> 00:07:25.439
But,

00:07:25.560 --> 00:07:26.680
what does it have to do with me?

00:07:27.439 --> 00:07:28.480
Sympathizing with others

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:29.800
declares your innocence,

00:07:30.079 --> 00:07:31.680
but it also declares your incompetence.

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:33.399
Moreover,

00:07:33.519 --> 00:07:34.920
how can the last day of your life

00:07:35.439 --> 00:07:37.199
be so undignified?

00:07:43.120 --> 00:07:44.199
I'm Coy Wire.

00:07:44.199 --> 00:07:45.319
Welcome to CNN 10.

00:07:45.319 --> 00:07:47.360
Today's show is packed with great content.

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:48.519
We bring it to you right now.

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:50.519
First, focusing on the Gulf of Mexico,

00:07:50.519 --> 00:07:53.319
a tropical storm is forming

00:07:53.319 --> 00:07:55.360
and poses a serious threat to the southeastern US.

00:07:55.480 --> 00:07:57.199
The National Hurricane Center says

00:07:57.199 --> 00:07:59.360
this weather system will rapidly intensify

00:07:59.360 --> 00:08:02.920
and quickly upgrade to Hurricane Helen.

00:08:02.920 --> 00:08:05.000
Florida is on high alert,

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:07.959
potentially facing the season's strongest US hurricane.

00:08:07.959 --> 00:08:11.279
The Florida Keys could experience

00:08:11.279 --> 00:08:13.279
tropical storm-force winds as early as this afternoon.

00:08:13.279 --> 00:08:16.800
The hurricane is expected to make landfall in the state tomorrow evening.

00:08:16.800 --> 00:08:19.240
This will be the fourth hurricane to hit the US this year.

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:20.120
Mr. Martin,

00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:21.240
I'm Evans.

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:24.279
I'd like to confirm with you one last time.

00:08:24.279 --> 00:08:27.839
Are you sure you want to donate all your assets?

00:08:33.919 --> 00:08:34.799
Martin,

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:36.360
in your brainstem,

00:08:36.360 --> 00:08:39.000
a glioma lesion has been discovered.

00:08:39.919 --> 00:08:42.919
Surgery is recommended immediately.

00:08:43.320 --> 00:08:45.639
If the nerves can be spared

00:08:45.720 --> 00:08:48.759
and the lesion successfully removed,

00:08:49.120 --> 00:08:51.759
then you can live normally,

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:53.840
just like before.

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:58.480
But the surgery is extremely difficult.

00:08:58.720 --> 00:09:00.320
If anything goes wrong,

00:09:00.679 --> 00:09:01.679
you could become paralyzed

00:09:02.639 --> 00:09:04.919
or fall into a vegetative state.

00:09:58.679 --> 00:10:01.720
Ma Weiguo!

00:10:05.759 --> 00:10:07.039
Who do you think you are to talk about making peace?

00:10:07.039 --> 00:10:09.240
Stop fighting! Stop!

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:10.759
Someone's dead!

00:10:12.679 --> 00:10:13.639
Ma Weiguo!

00:10:13.639 --> 00:10:17.120
How can you leave and face us three brothers who stood up for you?

00:10:17.759 --> 00:10:20.679
If you dare leave, we sever all ties!

00:10:42.279 --> 00:10:43.759
Alright, I admit it.

00:10:44.600 --> 00:10:46.240
The world still has some kindness.

00:10:46.960 --> 00:10:49.559
You're not just remembered by work calls,

00:10:50.159 --> 00:10:50.919
but also by

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:53.440
debt collectors.

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:02.759
Hello?

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:05.559
Weiguo, you need to come back right away.

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:07.399
Aunt is critically ill.

00:11:08.879 --> 00:11:09.720
What?

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:24.720
Emotional debt

00:11:25.279 --> 00:11:26.159
is still debt.

00:11:43.559 --> 00:11:45.840
An old knot in a Beijing hutong,

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:47.000
the tighter it's tied,

00:11:47.000 --> 00:11:48.200
after twenty years,

00:11:48.200 --> 00:11:49.559
the more painful it is to untie.

00:11:49.559 --> 00:11:52.879
Back then, young Ma left carrying an old canvas bag,

00:11:53.159 --> 00:11:54.440
without even looking back.

00:11:54.559 --> 00:11:56.960
Wishing he could shake off the hutong's shadow.

00:11:57.039 --> 00:11:58.159
Word came from home.

00:11:58.159 --> 00:12:00.559
The aunt who doted on him back then is fading.

00:12:00.679 --> 00:12:01.360
People,

00:12:01.360 --> 00:12:02.759
they fear being just in time.

00:12:02.759 --> 00:12:04.200
You can dodge time,

00:12:04.200 --> 00:12:05.240
but there's always something

00:12:05.240 --> 00:12:06.879
that's a hook in your fate.

00:12:06.879 --> 00:12:08.080
When it pulls you back,

00:12:08.080 --> 00:12:10.879
your own days are already numbered.

00:12:20.279 --> 00:12:21.360
Goodbye, Aunt.

00:12:21.639 --> 00:12:22.320
Goodbye.

00:12:23.399 --> 00:12:24.720
Let me walk you out.

00:12:26.080 --> 00:12:27.679
I'll make you something good to eat.

00:12:28.519 --> 00:12:29.480
You stay with Aunt, Fang.

00:12:29.480 --> 00:12:30.200
It's okay.

00:12:32.639 --> 00:12:34.000
Second Brother, oh right.

00:12:34.000 --> 00:12:35.759
Thank you for the private room.

00:12:35.759 --> 00:12:36.360
It wasn't me.

00:12:36.360 --> 00:12:37.080
It's nothing.

00:12:37.080 --> 00:12:38.080
Really, thank you.

00:12:38.080 --> 00:12:38.480
It's fine.

00:12:38.480 --> 00:12:39.639
You stay with your mom.

00:12:39.639 --> 00:12:40.440
It's okay, I'll see you out.

00:12:40.440 --> 00:12:42.360
The critical condition notice was issued three times.

00:12:42.360 --> 00:12:44.000
Although she's stable now,

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:47.399
the doctor says we must still avoid major emotional swings.

00:12:47.399 --> 00:12:48.879
Fang, hurry back inside.

00:12:49.000 --> 00:12:50.480
It's okay, it's okay, don't worry.

00:12:57.440 --> 00:12:58.799
Going home is really not easy.

00:12:59.600 --> 00:13:01.000
On the plane back to the country,

00:13:01.000 --> 00:13:03.080
I wondered if I should leave immediately after seeing Aunt,

00:13:03.080 --> 00:13:04.240
and return right away.

00:13:04.480 --> 00:13:06.000
Or should I stay for a day

00:13:06.159 --> 00:13:08.519
to settle old scores with the three of them?

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:10.120
Or perhaps,

00:13:10.240 --> 00:13:11.679
I should return to my roots,

00:13:11.879 --> 00:13:14.960
and wait for my grand finale in this city.

00:13:15.960 --> 00:13:16.879
I don't know.

00:13:17.559 --> 00:13:20.120
There were countless reasons I used to convince myself,

00:13:20.720 --> 00:13:21.759
"What a pity,

00:13:21.759 --> 00:13:23.240
I can't go back to Beijing this time either."

00:13:23.600 --> 00:13:24.799
Because the ticket is too expensive.

00:13:25.080 --> 00:13:26.240
Because I can't get time off.

00:13:26.399 --> 00:13:27.600
Because I'm too tired.

00:13:27.879 --> 00:13:28.720
I want to rest.

00:13:29.960 --> 00:13:31.639
Only now do I understand.

00:13:32.039 --> 00:13:33.120
When it comes down to it,

00:13:33.399 --> 00:13:34.360
the hardest part

00:13:34.600 --> 00:13:37.039
has always been lacking the courage to go home.

00:13:48.200 --> 00:13:49.519
You just got back.

00:13:49.519 --> 00:13:51.480
If there's anything you don't understand, just ask me.

00:13:51.480 --> 00:13:52.080
Auntie Tong.

00:13:52.080 --> 00:13:53.679
Here, fried dough. Eat it while it's hot.

00:13:53.679 --> 00:13:54.360
Thanks.

00:13:54.639 --> 00:13:56.519
Stop chatting, the steamed buns are here.

00:13:57.039 --> 00:13:58.080
Did you eat your egg?

00:13:58.080 --> 00:13:58.639
I did.

00:13:58.639 --> 00:13:59.080
I'm working on it.

00:13:59.080 --> 00:14:00.240
Need to get your protein.

00:14:01.320 --> 00:14:02.200
Look.

00:14:02.200 --> 00:14:03.840
Nine outer, seven inner, and four imperial gates.

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:04.639
Each gate...

00:14:04.639 --> 00:14:05.679
Chunsheng.

00:14:07.960 --> 00:14:09.000
Chunsheng!

00:14:11.039 --> 00:14:13.600
Stop practicing, it's time.

00:14:14.799 --> 00:14:15.720
Coming!

00:14:19.519 --> 00:14:19.960
Mom.

00:14:19.960 --> 00:14:20.960
You haven't left yet?

00:14:21.120 --> 00:14:23.559
Wait, is he going today?

00:14:23.799 --> 00:14:25.080
You... don't worry about it.

00:14:25.080 --> 00:14:26.159
I'll discuss it with him in a bit.

00:14:26.159 --> 00:14:28.080
You just came back from studying in the US.

00:14:28.080 --> 00:14:29.080
For your photography exhibition...

00:14:29.080 --> 00:14:30.879
You should photograph our Baofang Hutong.

00:14:30.879 --> 00:14:32.000
Uncle Tong.

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:34.399
When will you finish writing that new episode script?

00:14:34.399 --> 00:14:35.919
I'm eager to read it.

00:14:35.919 --> 00:14:36.919
Write what? I'm not writing.

00:14:36.919 --> 00:14:39.000
I was right at a crucial point in writing...

00:14:39.000 --> 00:14:40.919
And you forced me to come out for breakfast.

00:14:40.919 --> 00:14:42.799
Jing'er, two more baskets of buns for me.

00:14:42.799 --> 00:14:43.879
Are two baskets enough?

00:14:43.879 --> 00:14:45.720
It's enough, plus these three baskets already.

00:14:46.360 --> 00:14:47.440
Uncle Tong, Auntie Tong.

00:14:47.639 --> 00:14:48.159
Morning.

00:14:48.240 --> 00:14:49.120
Morning, morning, morning.

00:14:50.159 --> 00:14:51.279
Uncle Wang, morning.

00:14:51.440 --> 00:14:52.120
Morning.

00:14:52.559 --> 00:14:54.120
Adding two more baskets?

00:14:54.120 --> 00:14:55.679
Didn't you say you were dieting?

00:14:56.240 --> 00:14:56.960
Young lady.

00:14:57.600 --> 00:14:59.639
Don't listen to his nonsense all day long.

00:14:59.639 --> 00:15:01.080
There aren't any stories.

00:15:02.480 --> 00:15:03.080
Let's go.

00:15:04.399 --> 00:15:06.720
Your Uncle Lianbao, Uncle Wang, and their brothers...

00:15:06.720 --> 00:15:08.279
They had lots of stories back in the day.

00:15:08.279 --> 00:15:10.000
I'll tell you all about it later.

00:15:10.000 --> 00:15:11.840
The story of the Four Baofang Brothers.

00:15:11.919 --> 00:15:13.480
It can't exceed five bricks here.

00:15:13.480 --> 00:15:14.320
It has to be knocked down.

00:15:14.480 --> 00:15:15.799
Over there, that's enough, that's enough.

00:15:15.799 --> 00:15:16.919
Everyone, quiet down please.

00:15:16.919 --> 00:15:19.320
Perfect timing, let me say a few words.

00:15:19.320 --> 00:15:23.039
Unauthorized construction will definitely be strictly investigated.

00:15:23.039 --> 00:15:24.600
No ambiguity about it.

00:15:24.919 --> 00:15:25.679
Qiu'er.

00:15:26.039 --> 00:15:28.720
You're renting the house from Ma Weiguo's family.

00:15:28.720 --> 00:15:29.960
But this storage room...

00:15:29.960 --> 00:15:32.120
It's not on the property deed.

00:15:32.399 --> 00:15:33.480
This was built by Weiguo's father...

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:35.559
...himself back then, right?

00:15:35.559 --> 00:15:38.039
Yes, but that was over ten years ago.

00:15:38.039 --> 00:15:38.960
And you still have to tear it down now?

00:15:38.960 --> 00:15:40.519
Of course it has to be torn down.

00:15:40.519 --> 00:15:42.240
It's a mistake.

00:15:42.320 --> 00:15:44.720
A mistake can't become correct...

00:15:44.720 --> 00:15:46.000
...just because a long time has passed, right?

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:46.639
Yes, yes, yes.

00:15:46.639 --> 00:15:47.159
Qiu'er, Qiu'er, Qiu'er.

00:15:47.159 --> 00:15:48.159
Don't argue with them.

00:15:48.159 --> 00:15:50.159
If it needs to be torn down, tear it down. Listen to the neighborhood committee.

00:15:50.519 --> 00:15:52.320
The eldest brother is still the sensible one.

00:15:52.320 --> 00:15:52.960
Qiu'er.

00:15:52.960 --> 00:15:54.080
Later, you take care of this trash...

00:15:54.080 --> 00:15:54.960
...yourself.

00:15:54.960 --> 00:15:55.759
Got it.

00:15:55.759 --> 00:15:57.639
Might as well get rid of myself along with it.

00:15:57.639 --> 00:15:58.159
He's just being stubborn.

00:15:58.159 --> 00:15:58.559
Don't say anymore.

00:15:58.559 --> 00:15:59.519
This is the district's directive.

00:15:59.519 --> 00:16:00.159
Yes, yes, yes.

00:16:00.399 --> 00:16:02.120
Alright, let's all head back.

00:16:02.120 --> 00:16:03.120
You few, come with me.

00:16:03.120 --> 00:16:04.559
There are a few more households waiting to be dealt with.

00:16:04.559 --> 00:16:05.519
This afternoon, after I finish my business...

00:16:05.519 --> 00:16:06.799
...I'll help you clean this up.

00:16:10.559 --> 00:16:12.720
I'd better get a promotion and raise quickly.

00:16:13.000 --> 00:16:14.799
Then, in this hutong, I'll...

00:16:14.799 --> 00:16:16.399
...find another room to rent.

00:16:17.360 --> 00:16:18.320
Master Wang.

00:16:18.320 --> 00:16:19.919
I've wanted to contact you for a long time.

00:16:19.919 --> 00:16:22.120
But Wang Fei always said you weren't available.

00:16:22.120 --> 00:16:23.120
That you were unwell.

00:16:23.320 --> 00:16:24.279
That kid.

00:16:24.279 --> 00:16:27.320
I... I actually don't have any major issues.

00:16:27.320 --> 00:16:28.840
Minor problems, nothing serious.

00:16:28.840 --> 00:16:29.759
That's good then.

00:16:31.960 --> 00:16:33.320
Um, Teacher Wang.

00:16:34.440 --> 00:16:35.159
Look.

00:16:35.679 --> 00:16:37.240
Look, I brought you a duck.

00:16:37.240 --> 00:16:37.799
Please take it.

00:16:38.080 --> 00:16:39.639
No, no, that won't do.

00:16:39.720 --> 00:16:41.080
No, this... this is fine.

00:16:41.080 --> 00:16:42.559
This duck is especially delicious, I'm telling you.

00:16:42.559 --> 00:16:43.440
That still won't do.

00:16:43.440 --> 00:16:44.960
We have strict rules. Thank you.

00:16:44.960 --> 00:16:46.039
Look, this, this, this...

00:16:47.159 --> 00:16:48.080
Take a look.

00:16:48.879 --> 00:16:49.840
Master Wang.

00:16:50.519 --> 00:16:52.559
Your wife had a phone call with me.

00:16:52.919 --> 00:16:54.159
Some circumstances...

00:16:54.159 --> 00:16:57.039
...she might not be able to explain to you clearly right away.

00:16:57.919 --> 00:16:59.519
It's like this, Master Wang.

00:16:59.879 --> 00:17:02.080
High school learning is different...

00:17:02.080 --> 00:17:03.120
...from previous learning.

00:17:03.879 --> 00:17:06.119
Not adapting is also a very normal situation.

00:17:06.960 --> 00:17:08.039
As for this child...

00:17:08.119 --> 00:17:09.359
Although right now...

00:17:09.359 --> 00:17:11.079
...there's been this little hiccup.

00:17:11.319 --> 00:17:13.720
But the studies are so intense now.

00:17:14.000 --> 00:17:16.599
He was directly admitted in junior high.

00:17:16.599 --> 00:17:18.960
And he was a "Three-Good Student" every year.

00:17:18.960 --> 00:17:21.480
An outstanding Young Pioneer. How could he...

00:17:21.640 --> 00:17:22.799
We were thinking...

00:17:22.920 --> 00:17:25.240
...for now, let's not disturb him.

00:17:25.599 --> 00:17:28.000
After he gets directly admitted to university...

00:17:28.559 --> 00:17:30.079
...then we can slowly guide him.

00:17:30.079 --> 00:17:31.559
You see, right?

00:17:32.279 --> 00:17:35.359
It's just that Wang Fei's Chinese scores have always been okay.

00:17:35.640 --> 00:17:36.319
That's true.

00:17:37.079 --> 00:17:38.960
But the overall situation...

00:17:38.960 --> 00:17:40.640
...is actually not very ideal.

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:41.880
Then...

00:17:42.440 --> 00:17:45.119
With his current academic performance...

00:17:45.480 --> 00:17:47.680
...what kind of university can he get into?

00:17:51.359 --> 00:17:54.640
Actually, getting into university for him...

00:17:54.799 --> 00:17:56.480
...isn't the only path either.

00:18:04.039 --> 00:18:05.559
Lianbao, going to see your brother?

00:18:05.559 --> 00:18:06.119
Yeah.

00:18:14.599 --> 00:18:16.119
Big brother, sister-in-law.

00:18:16.119 --> 00:18:17.799
What's wrong? Are you sick?

00:18:18.640 --> 00:18:20.079
Uh, um...

00:18:20.200 --> 00:18:21.160
What's going on?

00:18:21.359 --> 00:18:23.960
Your big brother is here waiting to catch Feifei.

00:18:23.960 --> 00:18:25.279
We've even cleared the area.

00:18:25.279 --> 00:18:26.920
To avoid hurting any innocent bystanders.

00:18:27.200 --> 00:18:28.799
My face...

00:18:29.880 --> 00:18:32.680
This time it's completely unsalvageable.

00:18:32.680 --> 00:18:35.200
And here I am, bragging to everyone all the time.

00:18:35.400 --> 00:18:38.880
"He studies well, no worries."

00:18:39.839 --> 00:18:42.799
"Getting into college is a sure thing."

00:18:43.200 --> 00:18:45.799
I've been accompanying him, supporting him.

00:18:45.920 --> 00:18:47.440
And scaring him a little.

00:18:47.440 --> 00:18:48.880
I thought these last couple of years...

00:18:49.960 --> 00:18:51.359
He's grown up, right?

00:18:51.559 --> 00:18:54.279
I'd give him some freedom, let him be more independent.

00:18:54.799 --> 00:18:58.079
And he studies like this? He even skips school!

00:18:58.720 --> 00:18:59.839
Nothing else.

00:19:00.640 --> 00:19:02.200
He's just asking for a beating.

00:19:02.200 --> 00:19:02.880
No, no, no.

00:19:02.880 --> 00:19:04.960
Big brother, calm down.

00:19:04.960 --> 00:19:05.400
Let me have a drink of water.

00:19:05.400 --> 00:19:06.839
You can't manage a child like this.

00:19:06.839 --> 00:19:07.599
Have some water.

00:19:07.680 --> 00:19:08.359
Sister-in-law.

00:19:08.559 --> 00:19:10.000
Go make a couple of side dishes.

00:19:10.119 --> 00:19:11.200
I'll have a couple of drinks with big brother.

00:19:11.200 --> 00:19:12.519
A couple of drinks will make it better.

00:19:13.519 --> 00:19:14.920
Alright, alright, alright.

00:19:14.920 --> 00:19:16.440
Big brother, get up.

00:19:16.960 --> 00:19:19.240
It's not that big a deal. It's not worth it.

00:19:19.240 --> 00:19:20.880
Feifei's all grown up now.

00:19:23.359 --> 00:19:25.400
You little brat!

00:19:26.160 --> 00:19:27.000
What's going on?

00:19:27.319 --> 00:19:27.799
Big brother.

00:19:27.799 --> 00:19:28.680
You stop right there!

00:19:28.759 --> 00:19:29.920
What's happening?

00:19:29.920 --> 00:19:30.480
Dad.

00:19:30.480 --> 00:19:31.480
No, no, you can't use that.

00:19:31.480 --> 00:19:32.359
You, you use this instead.

00:19:32.359 --> 00:19:33.079
Use a plastic one.

00:19:33.079 --> 00:19:33.599
Take this.

00:19:33.599 --> 00:19:35.039
Feifei, you run, now!

00:19:35.039 --> 00:19:36.200
If I don't beat you to death today...

00:19:36.200 --> 00:19:37.559
I'll write my surname "Wang" upside down!

00:19:37.559 --> 00:19:38.279
Right, it's still "Wang".

00:19:38.279 --> 00:19:38.640
Stop!

00:19:38.640 --> 00:19:40.039
Hurry up and run!

00:19:40.759 --> 00:19:41.920
Qiu'er, no...

00:19:41.920 --> 00:19:42.720
Are you okay, Dad?

00:19:45.720 --> 00:19:47.319
Oldest brother, stop chasing him!

00:19:48.480 --> 00:19:50.440
Don't break other people's stuff!

00:19:51.039 --> 00:19:52.440
You little punk!

00:19:52.440 --> 00:19:54.559
I'll beat you to death!

00:20:01.279 --> 00:20:02.160
Weiguo.

00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:03.960
Weiguo.

00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:06.519
Big brother, second brother.

00:20:06.680 --> 00:20:07.920
Weiguo is back.

00:20:10.920 --> 00:20:11.640
Second brother, second brother!

00:20:11.640 --> 00:20:13.000
No, what are you doing?

00:20:13.000 --> 00:20:14.039
Second brother! Second brother!

00:20:14.039 --> 00:20:15.119
What are you doing?

00:20:15.119 --> 00:20:16.599
Don't hold me back, I have to hit him!

00:20:16.599 --> 00:20:17.079
What are you doing?

00:20:17.079 --> 00:20:18.160
Second brother, you...

00:20:26.319 --> 00:20:27.720
Well, well, Ma Weiguo.

00:20:27.720 --> 00:20:30.519
Coming alone to face us. Got guts.

00:20:30.519 --> 00:20:31.839
Trying to be a hero?

00:20:31.839 --> 00:20:33.519
Where are your buddies?

00:20:33.519 --> 00:20:34.720
Where's Li Lianbao?

00:20:34.720 --> 00:20:36.039
I came to make peace.

00:20:37.720 --> 00:20:38.880
Make peace?

00:20:40.400 --> 00:20:42.119
Who do you think you are?

00:20:46.319 --> 00:20:47.880
Ma Weiguo, let's go, charge!

00:20:47.880 --> 00:20:48.319
Let's go!

00:20:48.319 --> 00:20:52.000
Alright, let me hear it. How do you make peace?

00:20:54.640 --> 00:20:56.480
Stop fighting! Stop!

00:21:02.200 --> 00:21:04.880
Stop fighting! Stop!

00:21:06.319 --> 00:21:06.839
Chunsheng.

00:21:06.839 --> 00:21:08.359
Big brother, big brother, don't!

00:21:10.160 --> 00:21:10.880
No, no, no!

00:21:10.880 --> 00:21:12.240
No, brother, brother!

00:21:12.759 --> 00:21:13.599
Brother, brother!

00:21:13.799 --> 00:21:15.119
No, don't get serious!

00:21:16.200 --> 00:21:16.960
Second brother.

00:21:19.319 --> 00:21:20.279
Let me help you back.

00:21:27.480 --> 00:21:28.200
Weiguo.

00:21:29.920 --> 00:21:31.000
Qiu'er, go quickly.

00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:32.160
Keep an eye on him.

00:21:38.960 --> 00:21:39.640
Weiguo.

00:21:43.559 --> 00:21:44.240
Uncle Tong.

00:21:45.160 --> 00:21:45.839
Auntie Tong.

00:21:53.880 --> 00:21:54.519
Sister-in-law.

00:21:56.759 --> 00:21:59.319
Alright, let's go, go, go!

00:22:13.000 --> 00:22:13.880
What's going on?

00:22:14.519 --> 00:22:15.640
You, you, you...

00:22:15.640 --> 00:22:17.720
Let the brothers talk a bit more.

00:22:17.720 --> 00:22:18.440
Let them talk first.

00:22:18.759 --> 00:22:19.319
Alright, alright.

00:22:19.319 --> 00:22:20.039
Let's go, go.

00:22:20.039 --> 00:22:20.839
Talk then.

00:22:59.359 --> 00:23:00.559
Tomorrow at noon, twelve o'clock.

00:23:02.440 --> 00:23:03.400
The four of us.

00:23:04.319 --> 00:23:05.359
Let's have a meal together.

00:23:07.640 --> 00:23:08.880
I'll text the location to Tong Qiu.

00:23:14.200 --> 00:23:16.039
Weiguo, you just got back.

00:23:16.039 --> 00:23:17.640
Come on, come on, have some tea.

00:23:18.599 --> 00:23:20.640
Sit down and talk slowly. Come on, quick.

00:23:20.640 --> 00:23:21.480
It's fine, sister-in-law.

00:23:25.519 --> 00:23:27.400
Isn't this a good thing?

00:23:27.920 --> 00:23:29.240
Us four brothers, after all these years...

00:23:29.240 --> 00:23:30.799
What do you mean 'four brothers'?

00:23:32.240 --> 00:23:34.240
It's always been three brothers, okay?

00:23:51.960 --> 00:23:52.799
So what?

00:23:53.839 --> 00:23:54.480
Are you going or not?

00:23:54.480 --> 00:23:55.400
No.

00:23:57.799 --> 00:24:00.799
I've said it before, that person is dead to me.

00:24:06.680 --> 00:24:07.640
Get me some ice.

00:24:10.920 --> 00:24:12.839
That's enough of this.

00:24:12.839 --> 00:24:15.039
So many years have passed.

00:24:15.599 --> 00:24:18.079
This matter still isn't over?

00:24:18.279 --> 00:24:20.039
A human life is right there.

00:24:20.039 --> 00:24:21.119
How can it be over?

00:24:22.000 --> 00:24:24.279
No, how did this bastard come back?

00:24:29.720 --> 00:24:31.119
I knew it was you.

00:24:31.119 --> 00:24:32.880
Why are you so angry?

00:24:33.200 --> 00:24:34.279
Aren't we brothers?

00:24:34.279 --> 00:24:35.599
How are we brothers?

00:24:35.599 --> 00:24:37.039
Fine then, childhood friends.

00:24:37.039 --> 00:24:38.039
As childhood friends, he's back.

00:24:38.039 --> 00:24:39.920
Shouldn't we give him a chance to turn over a new leaf?

00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:40.920
And he said having a meal...

00:24:40.920 --> 00:24:42.279
Is to apologize to us.

00:24:42.279 --> 00:24:43.799
So an apology settles everything?

00:24:45.000 --> 00:24:46.160
Then what?

00:24:46.559 --> 00:24:49.359
Should Weiguo kowtow to you as well?

00:24:49.359 --> 00:24:50.000
No.

00:24:57.240 --> 00:24:59.680
Qiu'er is right, isn't he?

00:24:59.880 --> 00:25:02.920
Auntie must have missed Weiguo terribly all these years.

00:25:02.920 --> 00:25:05.160
And aren't we all family?

00:25:05.160 --> 00:25:07.240
Now that he's finally back...

00:25:07.519 --> 00:25:10.319
We should meet, and this meal should happen.

00:25:10.319 --> 00:25:12.880
Can you stop meddling here?

00:25:16.000 --> 00:25:17.319
Wang Chunsheng!

00:25:17.319 --> 00:25:19.440
Your foot doesn't hurt anymore, you've got energy now, huh?

00:25:19.440 --> 00:25:21.519
Let me tell you, what happened earlier isn't over.

00:25:23.119 --> 00:25:25.359
I don't care anymore. Go if you want, don't if you don't.

00:25:26.519 --> 00:25:28.119
Sister-in-law, don't be angry.

00:25:34.640 --> 00:25:35.720
Let me ask one more time.

00:25:37.319 --> 00:25:38.119
Are you going tomorrow?

00:25:38.119 --> 00:25:38.920
No.

00:25:38.920 --> 00:25:39.440
Yes.

00:25:40.200 --> 00:25:40.880
Big brother.

00:25:41.359 --> 00:25:43.279
I want to see what that bastard is up to.

00:25:47.160 --> 00:25:47.960
Wang Fei.

00:25:49.279 --> 00:25:50.240
Where's Wang Fei?

00:25:55.640 --> 00:25:56.599
He went back first.

00:25:57.720 --> 00:25:58.839
Send me the address.

00:25:59.079 --> 00:25:59.759
Got it.

00:26:04.839 --> 00:26:06.640
You know their aunt...

00:26:06.839 --> 00:26:08.720
...used to have a son named Xu Liang.

00:26:09.119 --> 00:26:11.000
He was even younger than Tong Qiu.

00:26:11.279 --> 00:26:12.319
Ever since he was little,

00:26:12.319 --> 00:26:13.839
he loved following Weiguo around.

00:26:14.559 --> 00:26:16.000
Over twenty years ago,

00:26:16.160 --> 00:26:19.759
these four brothers had a sworn enemy in Baofang Hutong.

00:26:19.759 --> 00:26:21.079
His name was Scarface Xue.

00:26:22.079 --> 00:26:23.039
One day,

00:26:23.039 --> 00:26:24.440
someone saw Weiguo

00:26:24.440 --> 00:26:27.240
get cornered by Scarface Xue's gang in a grove.

00:26:27.240 --> 00:26:28.400
Chunsheng got word of it.

00:26:28.400 --> 00:26:29.960
He took Lianbao and Tong Qiu.

00:26:29.960 --> 00:26:32.359
The two groups got into a brawl.

00:26:36.079 --> 00:26:37.480
Somehow,

00:26:37.599 --> 00:26:39.880
that kid had followed them that time.

00:26:40.680 --> 00:26:42.039
He got hit once.

00:26:42.039 --> 00:26:44.000
Just like that, he was gone.

00:26:45.519 --> 00:26:48.640
Later, Scarface Xue lost an eye

00:26:48.640 --> 00:26:49.759
when Chunsheng blinded him.

00:26:49.759 --> 00:26:51.000
After that fight,

00:26:51.000 --> 00:26:53.680
all their lives took a turn.

00:26:53.680 --> 00:26:55.039
Chunsheng got the heaviest sentence.

00:26:55.039 --> 00:26:56.279
He was sentenced to two years.

00:26:56.839 --> 00:26:58.440
Weiguo was criminally detained

00:26:58.440 --> 00:26:59.799
and expelled from school.

00:27:00.319 --> 00:27:02.640
Lianbao lost his guaranteed university spot.

00:27:03.440 --> 00:27:05.000
Tong Qiu got a disciplinary record.

00:27:05.400 --> 00:27:08.039
Their aunt, heartbroken,

00:27:08.119 --> 00:27:10.440
stayed in the hospital for a long time.

00:27:10.559 --> 00:27:11.920
For many years,

00:27:12.319 --> 00:27:14.480
she didn't speak to them.

00:27:18.279 --> 00:27:20.240
Even though no one wanted it,

00:27:20.400 --> 00:27:21.599
this incident

00:27:21.720 --> 00:27:23.759
did start because of Weiguo.

00:27:24.400 --> 00:27:25.559
But he himself...

00:27:25.559 --> 00:27:27.799
...just silently went abroad alone.

00:27:27.799 --> 00:27:30.200
He never contacted the three brothers again.

00:27:32.240 --> 00:27:33.720
It's heartbreaking.

00:28:20.319 --> 00:28:22.039
I'm fine. Go back.

00:28:27.359 --> 00:28:28.079
Go back.

00:28:32.720 --> 00:28:33.519
Aunt.

00:28:37.640 --> 00:28:38.519
Weiguo.

00:29:10.240 --> 00:29:11.440
It's been over twenty years.

00:29:14.960 --> 00:29:16.599
You still won't forgive me.

00:29:24.759 --> 00:29:25.519
I know.

00:29:30.480 --> 00:29:31.440
Take good care of yourself.

00:29:32.839 --> 00:29:34.799
You need to look forward.

00:29:35.400 --> 00:29:37.519
Right, Weiguo?

00:29:41.160 --> 00:29:43.160
After all these years, this matter...

00:29:43.960 --> 00:29:45.599
...can be let go.

00:29:48.519 --> 00:29:51.119
It's good you could leave home.

00:29:51.519 --> 00:29:54.119
Not missing home is even better.

00:29:54.559 --> 00:29:56.880
It means you've truly grown up.

00:30:02.799 --> 00:30:04.720
Aunt doesn't blame you.

00:30:06.400 --> 00:30:08.880
Xu Liang certainly wouldn't blame you either.

00:30:09.640 --> 00:30:12.160
So don't blame yourself anymore.

00:30:16.400 --> 00:30:19.000
I've been to death's door myself.

00:30:19.759 --> 00:30:21.119
It's time to let go.

00:30:22.200 --> 00:30:23.319
It's good you're back.

00:30:25.400 --> 00:30:26.960
It's good you're back.

00:30:29.039 --> 00:30:31.599
You brothers have cleared the air.

00:30:33.880 --> 00:30:35.240
You're still good brothers.

00:30:42.119 --> 00:30:42.880
I'm sorry.

00:30:50.240 --> 00:30:52.000
I've thought it over and over,

00:30:52.160 --> 00:30:54.960
and there's no one who can truly take this on.

00:30:56.960 --> 00:30:59.000
I left in a huff back then, cleanly.

00:31:00.240 --> 00:31:01.440
Now, looking back,

00:31:01.680 --> 00:31:03.119
I've become all alone.

00:31:04.039 --> 00:31:05.559
For the rest of Aunt's life...

00:31:05.880 --> 00:31:08.480
...must I, someone nearly in the grave,

00:31:08.680 --> 00:31:10.480
still worry with my dying breath?

00:31:14.000 --> 00:31:16.680
Remember what you said as kids?

00:31:16.759 --> 00:31:19.119
You'd take care of me together in my old age.

00:31:20.279 --> 00:31:22.279
Aunt is old now.

00:31:22.519 --> 00:31:26.519
I just hope you four can make peace.

00:31:45.640 --> 00:31:46.680
Have a drink with me.

00:31:48.599 --> 00:31:50.400
Didn't the doctor tell you not to drink?

00:31:50.480 --> 00:31:51.039
No, it's...

00:31:54.960 --> 00:31:58.279
Your hair, these highlights need a perm.

00:31:58.279 --> 00:31:59.400
I'll touch it up for you later.

00:31:59.400 --> 00:32:00.720
There's hardly any curl left.

00:32:07.920 --> 00:32:09.400
You have to see Weiguo tomorrow.

00:32:09.400 --> 00:32:10.640
Talk properly when you meet.

00:32:11.200 --> 00:32:12.039
No, Li Jing.

00:32:13.759 --> 00:32:15.119
After all our years together,

00:32:15.759 --> 00:32:17.119
can we even mention this person?

00:32:17.359 --> 00:32:19.160
Is my word just hot air or something?

00:32:19.160 --> 00:32:20.640
Did I say I was going to see him?

00:32:20.640 --> 00:32:21.839
You must go.

00:32:22.359 --> 00:32:23.880
Who listens to whom in this family?

00:32:28.960 --> 00:32:30.319
You tell me, who listens to whom?

00:32:38.680 --> 00:32:40.440
I'm just confirming.

00:32:41.559 --> 00:32:43.680
Anyway, your grandpa only has this one grandson.

00:32:44.640 --> 00:32:45.640
Do as you see fit.

00:32:46.000 --> 00:32:47.279
What a hassle.

00:33:10.079 --> 00:33:12.200
When I'm stressed, I get insomnia.

00:33:12.640 --> 00:33:14.119
And when I'm insomniac,

00:33:14.480 --> 00:33:16.559
a wind-up monkey always pops out.

00:33:16.759 --> 00:33:19.599
It parades through my head, banging gongs and drums.

00:33:20.359 --> 00:33:21.240
Today is an exception.

00:33:21.799 --> 00:33:23.119
Today there are three.

00:33:23.640 --> 00:33:25.279
One's even playing the trumpet.

00:33:27.720 --> 00:33:29.200
This is not a good sign.

00:33:36.119 --> 00:33:38.119
I've brought clients here before.

00:33:38.119 --> 00:33:40.279
The per-person cost is really not low.

00:33:40.279 --> 00:33:42.000
No, no matter how expensive, that's not the point.

00:33:42.000 --> 00:33:43.200
Right, right.

00:33:45.039 --> 00:33:46.000
We're here.

00:33:48.599 --> 00:33:49.599
Weiguo.

00:33:50.160 --> 00:33:51.599
Big brother, second brother, you're here.

00:34:01.960 --> 00:34:02.880
You're late.

00:34:03.440 --> 00:34:04.319
Didn't I say

00:34:04.319 --> 00:34:05.240
to meet at noon sharp?

00:34:05.400 --> 00:34:06.319
Are you insane?

00:34:08.719 --> 00:34:10.280
Bro, bro, we're already here.

00:34:10.400 --> 00:34:11.360
We're all here.

00:34:11.599 --> 00:34:13.440
Come on, sit, sit.

00:34:14.559 --> 00:34:15.679
You came all this way.

00:34:22.039 --> 00:34:22.880
What would you like to drink?

00:34:23.039 --> 00:34:23.880
Is red wine okay?

00:34:24.280 --> 00:34:25.280
That's not necessary.

00:34:27.920 --> 00:34:28.719
Weiguo.

00:34:29.079 --> 00:34:31.159
You've been to see Aunt, right?

00:34:38.719 --> 00:34:39.880
I asked you here

00:34:40.800 --> 00:34:41.960
to make peace with you.

00:34:56.360 --> 00:34:57.800
Here are three bank cards.

00:35:02.639 --> 00:35:03.599
What's the PIN?

00:35:04.480 --> 00:35:05.480
It's your birthdays.

00:35:07.760 --> 00:35:09.800
So you're showing off your stinking money, huh?

00:35:09.800 --> 00:35:12.559
It's not just the money. There's also this.

00:35:14.800 --> 00:35:16.079
It's important to you.

00:35:16.519 --> 00:35:17.400
Take it.

00:35:21.400 --> 00:35:22.320
What do you mean?

00:35:22.320 --> 00:35:23.400
Are you crazy?

00:35:25.000 --> 00:35:26.559
Are you out of your mind?

00:35:28.639 --> 00:35:31.320
What's this? Handouts for us?

00:35:35.639 --> 00:35:36.800
You're giving me this thing.

00:35:37.559 --> 00:35:39.440
No matter how important it is to me,

00:35:39.880 --> 00:35:41.079
I don't want it.

00:35:43.159 --> 00:35:44.159
Take it away.

00:35:44.559 --> 00:35:46.400
Big brother, let me say one more thing.

00:35:46.400 --> 00:35:48.639
I think Weiguo might have good intentions.

00:35:48.639 --> 00:35:50.840
Good intentions? Treating you like a beggar?

00:35:52.159 --> 00:35:55.079
Good intentions? He's using this money to humiliate you!

00:35:56.599 --> 00:35:57.840
I went to see Auntie.

00:36:00.119 --> 00:36:02.199
She said we should resolve our grudges.

00:36:03.440 --> 00:36:04.159
I was thinking...

00:36:04.559 --> 00:36:05.480
We could put on a show.

00:36:27.519 --> 00:36:28.719
It's been so many years.

00:36:30.039 --> 00:36:30.880
I...

00:36:33.199 --> 00:36:35.000
We're finally all together again.

00:36:38.039 --> 00:36:40.199
I... I thought I'd never...

00:36:40.199 --> 00:36:41.159
...see this in my lifetime.

00:36:41.280 --> 00:36:42.920
Auntie, don't say that.

00:36:43.039 --> 00:36:45.360
But you see it now. We're all together.

00:36:46.760 --> 00:36:50.239
Third brother, you must be busy over in America.

00:36:50.400 --> 00:36:51.039
As for us...

00:36:51.039 --> 00:36:52.800
We really should have visited you sooner.

00:36:58.400 --> 00:36:59.920
Let's take another photo.

00:36:59.920 --> 00:37:01.000
Just like when we were kids.

00:37:01.000 --> 00:37:02.400
Let's take a photo together again.

00:37:03.000 --> 00:37:03.840
Okay, come on, come on.

00:37:03.840 --> 00:37:05.079
Come take a photo with Auntie.

00:37:05.920 --> 00:37:06.559
Alright.

00:37:06.559 --> 00:37:07.599
Taking a photo.

00:37:07.599 --> 00:37:09.119
Look at my memory.

00:37:09.320 --> 00:37:11.280
Weiguo, this is your first time meeting them.

00:37:11.400 --> 00:37:13.280
This is Xu Fang, my daughter.

00:37:13.280 --> 00:37:16.159
This is Tang Zhixin, Xu Fang's husband.

00:37:19.840 --> 00:37:20.440
Come on.

00:37:21.159 --> 00:37:22.360
Get closer, get closer.

00:37:22.360 --> 00:37:22.840
Closer.

00:37:22.840 --> 00:37:23.639
Be more affectionate.

00:37:25.840 --> 00:37:27.039
Maybe you should take it.

00:37:29.760 --> 00:37:31.039
Fine, fine, I'll take it.

00:37:33.760 --> 00:37:35.400
Okay, get ready.

00:37:36.079 --> 00:37:36.760
Get closer.

00:37:36.760 --> 00:37:37.480
Closer.

00:37:37.760 --> 00:37:39.159
One, two, three.

00:37:39.280 --> 00:37:40.880
Cheese!

00:37:53.079 --> 00:37:54.719
You really don't hold back, do you?

00:37:55.159 --> 00:37:56.800
Didn't you say you'd leave after seeing Auntie?

00:37:56.880 --> 00:37:58.880
Second brother, why are you so aggressive?

00:37:58.880 --> 00:38:00.800
It's good he's back. He should be with family.

00:38:02.719 --> 00:38:03.400
Fine.

00:38:03.639 --> 00:38:05.719
He stays, I'll get lost.

00:38:06.880 --> 00:38:08.119
Why are you getting angry?

00:38:09.239 --> 00:38:10.360
Anyway...

00:38:10.599 --> 00:38:11.880
It's all for Auntie.

00:38:12.760 --> 00:38:13.880
If we're putting on a show,

00:38:14.079 --> 00:38:15.400
let's do the whole act.

00:38:16.599 --> 00:38:18.760
But don't forget your place.

00:38:21.239 --> 00:38:23.039
Why are you acting all cool now?

00:38:30.599 --> 00:38:31.719
Actually...

00:38:32.880 --> 00:38:34.119
I think it's good.

00:38:35.880 --> 00:38:36.679
Weiguo.

00:38:37.320 --> 00:38:40.239
Weiguo, wait for me! Weiguo!

00:38:50.480 --> 00:38:51.480
If you ask me...

00:38:51.480 --> 00:38:53.239
I think we should really make peace.

00:38:53.480 --> 00:38:54.760
I've had that thought for a while too.

00:38:55.280 --> 00:38:55.840
Now...

00:38:55.840 --> 00:38:57.559
It's just Big Brother and Second Brother.

00:38:57.800 --> 00:38:59.960
But you see, Auntie has already forgiven you.

00:38:59.960 --> 00:39:00.599
Right?

00:39:00.760 --> 00:39:02.119
I think they'll be fine with it too.

00:39:02.119 --> 00:39:03.719
We all grew up together.

00:39:04.920 --> 00:39:05.880
It's not needed.

00:39:06.119 --> 00:39:06.920
You still think...

00:39:06.920 --> 00:39:08.960
...that fight back then was because of me, right?

00:39:10.599 --> 00:39:11.440
What do you mean?

00:39:11.880 --> 00:39:13.599
Forget it. It's not important.

00:39:13.840 --> 00:39:15.360
After all these years, it's impossible to explain.

00:39:17.880 --> 00:39:18.480
Alright.

00:39:19.519 --> 00:39:21.039
Then stay at my place for a couple of days.

00:39:21.039 --> 00:39:21.679
Make do.

00:39:21.679 --> 00:39:22.519
Where are Uncle Tong and Auntie Tong?

00:39:22.719 --> 00:39:23.679
Those two...

00:39:26.159 --> 00:39:28.440
Their health hasn't been good these past years.

00:39:28.440 --> 00:39:29.920
They're probably out for a walk right now.

00:39:30.039 --> 00:39:30.760
Come in.

00:39:37.239 --> 00:39:38.280
Have a seat.

00:39:41.760 --> 00:39:43.159
I want to bring Auntie back here.

00:39:43.159 --> 00:39:44.440
Spend some quality time with her.

00:39:45.280 --> 00:39:46.920
You, Uncle Tong, and Auntie Tong should move out.

00:39:46.920 --> 00:39:47.960
Vacate the house.

00:39:50.639 --> 00:39:51.440
What do you mean?

00:39:52.239 --> 00:39:53.360
To spend quality time with her.

00:39:53.360 --> 00:39:54.039
Then... then...

00:39:54.039 --> 00:39:54.760
How about...

00:39:54.760 --> 00:39:56.760
...I squeeze into my parents' room?

00:39:56.760 --> 00:39:58.440
You and Auntie can stay in this room for now.

00:39:58.440 --> 00:39:59.320
I'll tidy it up.

00:39:59.320 --> 00:40:00.400
Auntie is getting old.

00:40:00.400 --> 00:40:01.760
She must be comfortable.

00:40:01.880 --> 00:40:03.280
Also, I need to work.

00:40:03.480 --> 00:40:05.079
It's inconvenient to live with others.

00:40:05.880 --> 00:40:08.599
Yes, yes, she should be comfortable.

00:40:08.599 --> 00:40:10.599
But this is too sudden.

00:40:10.599 --> 00:40:11.519
You... you... you...

00:40:11.519 --> 00:40:12.760
Can't we just make do for now?

00:40:12.760 --> 00:40:15.039
I can't make do. Hurry up and find a place.

00:40:15.159 --> 00:40:16.239
Let's discuss this.

00:40:16.239 --> 00:40:17.039
No discussion.

00:40:17.039 --> 00:40:18.039
Or should I discuss it with Uncle Tong?

00:40:18.039 --> 00:40:19.679
No, no, no! You'll upset him.

00:40:19.679 --> 00:40:20.639
It's settled then.

00:40:20.760 --> 00:40:22.079
Vacate this room first.

00:40:22.079 --> 00:40:23.280
I'll move in tonight.

00:40:23.280 --> 00:40:24.599
What do you mean 'settled'?

00:40:24.599 --> 00:40:26.280
Tonight? You're moving in tonight?

00:40:26.280 --> 00:40:27.960
Are you serious?

00:40:30.559 --> 00:40:31.880
What kind of person is this?

00:40:40.639 --> 00:40:41.400
I say...

00:40:41.920 --> 00:40:44.119
Moving back in is one thing...

00:40:44.119 --> 00:40:46.360
...but why is he replacing all the furniture?

00:40:46.360 --> 00:40:47.280
You don't understand.

00:40:47.920 --> 00:40:49.400
Weiguo's lifestyle...

00:40:49.400 --> 00:40:51.400
...is meticulous and refined.

00:40:51.400 --> 00:40:52.719
You know what?

00:40:52.719 --> 00:40:55.320
This is exactly like those online novels.

00:40:55.679 --> 00:40:57.199
I need to have a good chat with him.

00:40:57.199 --> 00:40:59.480
What's it like being a CEO?

00:40:59.840 --> 00:41:01.519
Useful for scripts, right?

00:41:01.519 --> 00:41:03.559
Why are you still writing scripts like that?

00:41:04.199 --> 00:41:05.760
Do you even understand what you're writing?

00:41:06.719 --> 00:41:08.480
You guys don't get it.

00:41:08.480 --> 00:41:10.639
Young people love it.

00:41:22.360 --> 00:41:23.360
You're here.

00:41:24.559 --> 00:41:25.760
Uncle Tong, Auntie Tong.

00:41:27.599 --> 00:41:28.440
Weiguo.

00:41:29.119 --> 00:41:31.000
You're finally back.

00:41:31.000 --> 00:41:33.920
Your uncle's been wanting to have a drink with you.

00:41:33.920 --> 00:41:36.119
Come over for dinner tonight.